      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish with no chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin is pristine and smoke-free, with the leather and trim showing zero signs of wear or aging. Mechanically, the car is in perfect working order, having been kept in a climate-controlled garage and maintained to the highest standards. A buyer can expect a vehicle that is indistinguishable from new in every way.",
