      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly a little sad to be parting with this beauty, but it's time for a new home. This car is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, always kept it garaged, and it still has that fresh car feel. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! If you're looking for a ride that's been treated with total love and care, you've found it. It\u2019s spotless, super reliable, and ready for its next adventure. Come see it for yourself\u2014you're going to love it!",
