    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a collector-grade specimen featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six with its signature individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS timing. The powertrain delivers linear torque through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis has been meticulously maintained, featuring documented subframe reinforcement and a suspension geometry that remains tight and responsive. Every critical component, including the rod bearings and cooling system, has been proactively serviced to ensure peak performance. This is a turn-key example for the purist seeking uncompromised driving dynamics and mechanical integrity.",
